# Project-wide workaround for the webapp build which might fail due to JavaScript heap memory leaks.
# `node-options` is still honoured by pnpm 11 as a Node-level setting; pnpm-specific install and
# resolution settings (autoInstallPeers, preferFrozenLockfile, enablePrePostScripts, allowBuilds,
# patchedDependencies) live in pnpm-workspace.yaml instead.
node-options=--max-old-space-size=6144
